INFOMap made by Biohazard.pt Hello! This is my latest map, and it is Jail Break map. It is my first map in this mod, I have been making maps for different mods for a while. Hope you like it. This map was created for the portuguese FRAGXL.com community.
MAP INFOType: Jail Break Players: 48 max. - Ambient Sounds. - Custom Decals. - Awesome Skybox by karatek√§fer. - Sunny weather. - Big jail, Medic, Kitchen, Security, Armory, Last Request Zones, etc.
SCREENSHOT INFOScreenshot 1 - Cells Overview Screenshot 2 - Armory Screenshot 3 - Main entrance Screenshot 4 - Individual Cell Screenshot 5 - Outside Gate Screenshot 6 - Last Request Zone
If you want to post this map on other forums go ahead but give me credit for my own map. Thanks go to Unreal. Please feel free to rate, stamp or/and post some feedback.
